			(property "Description" "Reed Switch\n\nA reed switch is a magnetically-actuated switch. When the device is exposed to a magnetic field, the two ferrous materials inside the switch pull together and the switch closes.\n\nVariant Overview PTH-GLASS\n\n• https://www.sparkfun.com/products/8642 Reed Switch (COM-08642) - PTH reed switch w/ glass body (6.0 x 0.9 mm)\n\nPTH-INSULATED\n\n• https://www.sparkfun.com/products/10601 Reed Switch - Insulated (COM-10601) - PTH reed switch w/ insulated body (15.1 x 4.2 mm)"
